CANRY DEPLOYMENT
+++++++++++++++
Add a label to the matLabels and template date to differentiate canry and make it easier for debugging:

spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: myapp
      version: canary
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: myapp
        version: canary


Keep app: myapp SAME as main (so Service balances traffic)
Add version: canary to distinguish
Selector must match template labels exactly
